\begin_layout Standard
Each of the planes can be used for different operations.
 For example we use the first plane for threshold estimation for the subsequent
 molecular detection step.
 We use the second plane (or if selected by the user, the third plane) as
 an input image for the detection of molecules.
\end_layout

